{"tid":814343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞女乘客與的士司機嘈 重慶大廈吹雞 撲出近數十人","createTime":"2018-09-11T07:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T17:19:45.000Z","uid":54373,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7e37d51869f8ce4e6319a2badd66b635c0866ad1","tid":814343,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180911/large/1536642137_4dd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180911%2Flarge%2F1536642137_4dd9.jpg&h=04e4a1f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名的士司機，昨晚載着醉酒女乘客到尖沙嘴彌敦道重慶大廈，被對方指偷去她遺在車廂的手機。雙方起爭執互相拉扯，一度滾在地上「碌地沙」。重慶大廈附近的南亞漢，以為女同鄉被欺侮，撲出包圍的士司機，一時間群情洶湧。<br />\n<br />\n讀者陳先生當時途經現場，目擊女乘客和司機爭執拉扯，雙雙倒地，要車上的男乘客落車將他們分開。當時近百人圍觀，當中數十人包圍住的士。而的士司機的T裇已經被扯爛露出左肩，氣氛緊張。幸警員迅速趕到，手持盾牌控制場面。陳先生聽到的士司機向警員說：「話我偷電話呀！」<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆查詢稱，昨晚8時左右，南亞裔女乘客在深水埗乘的士到重慶大廈，到埗後落車，但隨即發現不見了手機，懷疑遺留在的士上，折返找尋，但沒有發現，因而與姓倪(56歲)司機起爭執。據悉，女乘客滿身酒氣，加上語言不通，雙方無法溝通，經警員調查，司機頸紅拒絕送院，並不追究，事件中無人被捕。"},{"pid":"9c72e18e880ea4f75d9924e9cb8df8a2e9c2a8f7","tid":814343,"uid":41508,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44545fa0e4b3a6ee7ced7c5ecbcb47d33826841e","tid":814343,"uid":43041,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"的狗 vs 蝻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/153821_c3b990e765581875fa691fa86c788716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F153821_c3b990e765581875fa691fa86c788716.jpg&h=749c7c30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb578423b06513886dbd113304af9e237a05ce3f","tid":814343,"uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"南亞人老屈香港人,再<span style=\"color: red;\">襲擊</span><br />\n警員迅速趕到，手持盾牌<span style=\"color: red;\">控制場面</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有冇拉到人? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc13ad700f99c91535f90a497d753297d3307b7","tid":814343,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"ade8eef79d407006a053af3f0017acb598a7e4a9","tid":814343,"uid":208726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc63ea2dd6370620bc8f49f3ced204b13271005b","tid":814343,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ade8eef79d407006a053af3f0017acb598a7e4a9","tid":814343,"uid":208726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"現在沒有，將來不知道。。。。"},{"pid":"4a4d3209c99c96bc8dc1ea1f28f5df28fdeae235","tid":814343,"uid":55571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ade8eef79d407006a053af3f0017acb598a7e4a9","tid":814343,"uid":208726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"如果呢班係黃絲<br />\n香港....."},{"pid":"97f09d40473f291477db2889504b177d85d1ee5e","tid":814343,"uid":189465,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ade8eef79d407006a053af3f0017acb598a7e4a9","tid":814343,"uid":208726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"香港人個個自撚私<br />\n唔撚屌鳩自己人已經偷笑<br />\n仲求團結？人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"9fd643f09904f7651d394be5a83156b7e1317189","tid":814343,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:03:10.000Z","msg":"遲早黎次水晶之夜翻版"},{"pid":"b5a19a974c4fdfeb900ce4aa49c8b01cfcdce85f","tid":814343,"uid":156972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade8eef79d407006a053af3f0017acb598a7e4a9","tid":814343,"uid":208726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:56:01.000Z","msg